rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0001
rows.name: Commander Vandham, we've just returned![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0002
rows.name: Iriina already came by to report.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0003
rows.name: Impressive. Returning unharmed, all of you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0004
rows.name: But the Database Unit was destroyed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0005
rows.name:
And so, another piece
of Earth's heritage is lost.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0006
rows.name: It's unfortunate, but better than losing crew members.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0007
rows.name:
Alright, let's go eat.
My treat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0008
rows.name: You guys helped me out this time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0009
rows.name: That's unusual.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0010
rows.name: Really unusual.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0011
rows.name: Indeed unusual, meh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0012
rows.name: Ngh[ST:wide ]â€• The three of you, all at once...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0017
rows.name:
But really, don't say things like "thanks,"
it's not like you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0018
rows.name: But this is an unknown planet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0019
rows.name:
We don't know when we might end up
in the same situation as Iriina's team.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0020
rows.name: Yeah, true, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0021
rows.name: Lin-san's cooking is the best, meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0022
rows.name: Tatsu, good point![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0023
rows.name: Today, I'll throw in dessert specially for you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0024
rows.name: Meh-meh-meh-meh-meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0025
rows.name: See?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0026
rows.name: Guess I can't compete with Lin's cooking.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0027
rows.name: Commander Vandham, please come eat too![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs07080100_MSG0028
rows.name: Yeah, got it.[ST:wait ]
